modShortDescription: Adds a Writable Storage Box tier 2, which has more storage at a slightly higher resource cost. The original Writable Storage Box is still there, unchanged.
modDescription:
Adds a Writable Storage Box tier 2, which has more [storage](https://7daystodiemods.com/tag/7-days-to-die-storage/) at a slightly higher resource cost. The original Writable Storage Box is still there, unchanged.

**[Download](https://github.com/Alyssuu/Bigger-Writable-Storage-Boxes/raw/main/Alyssas%20scuffed%20storage%20VANILLA.zip)** Vanilla version with 100 slots _(recommended)_  
**[Download](https://github.com/Alyssuu/Bigger-Writable-Storage-Boxes-DF/raw/main/Alyssas%20scuffed%20storage%20DF.zip)** Version for Darkness Falls _(it has 120 slots so its exactly the same size as the “lockables” there, do not use in vanilla, it will not work.)_

**Credits:** Alyssa, Everyone who helped me from Guppy’s modding Discord
